This paper deals with wireless systems and communication, which falls under the Information Theory (cs.IT) and Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI) categories. The paper also discusses energy efficiency and power consumption, which could fall under the Systems and Control (cs.SY) category. The specific wireless systems mentioned, such as millimeter wave and massive MIMO, could also place this paper under the Multimedia (cs.MM) and Architecture (cs.AR) categories.
